                Read our privacy notice for further information.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="homepage__data-selection__upload-wrapper"><a
                class="homepage__data-selection__upload-button js-dataset-upload" href="{{ url_for('home.about') }}#data-upload">Privacy notice</a></div>
    </div>
</div>